&lt;li&gt;Select appropriate methodologies based on business objectives and research questions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop research plans, screeners, discussion guides, questionnaires, and study materials.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct field-based consumer research in retail and customer environments when needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consumer &amp;amp; Market Insights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
