&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated proficiency in &lt;strong&gt;R&lt;/strong&gt;, particularly the &lt;strong&gt;Tidyverse&lt;/strong&gt; ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in survey design, item development, and large‑scale data collection.&lt;/li&gt;
