&lt;h3&gt;Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We are seeking an experienced and strategic Global Partner Marketing Manager to drive partner enablement, co-marketing initiatives, executive engagement programs, and cross-functional program management across a global ecosystem of enterprise technology partners and Systems Integrators.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;This is a highly visible role operating at the intersection of AI, enterprise technology, and strategic partnerships. The ideal candidate brings a strong background in partner marketing, alliance marketing, or ecosystem marketing, along with exceptional program management and stakeholder engagement skills. Success in this role requires adaptability, a collaborative mindset, and the ability to thrive in a fast-paced, evolving environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Partner Enablement&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute partner enablement programs, training initiatives, and go-to-market strategies for strategic enterprise partners and Systems Integrators.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create scalable frameworks and resources that accelerate partner adoption and engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Co-Marketing Programs&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the planning and execution of joint marketing initiatives with global partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive integrated campaigns, events, and partner-led marketing activities that support ecosystem growth and business objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Executive Engagement&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage executive engagement programs with senior partner stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate strategic meetings, communications, and relationship-building initiatives that strengthen partner alignment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Cross-Functional Program Management&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with internal marketing, product, sales, partnerships, and operations teams to ensure alignment on priorities, timelines, and deliverables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage multiple complex initiatives simultaneously while maintaining attention to detail and execution excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Partner Ecosystem Growth&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the development and expansion of strategic partner relationships through marketing programs and ecosystem engagement activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage partner insights and performance data to inform strategy and optimize program effectiveness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Required Qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of experience in B2B marketing, partner marketing, alliance marketing, channel marketing, or enterprise technology marketing.&lt;/li&gt;
